_sText:
This is a remake of an old TacOps map which you may or (probably) may not remember. Credit goes to the guy who designed the original version of this map (sorry I don't know his name). I need your comments, suggestions, and complaints so I can incorporate them all into a final version of this map.

I will also try to work on the navigation mesh to assist the bots and hostages so they should be smarter in the final version. I have received little feedback on this map so I will try and see how it goes here.
